{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"deeacc71b6","title":"江青张春桥姚文元在批判《园丁之歌》稿件上的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6a9372823e","index":0,"year":1973,"month":7,"day":28,"articleId":"deeacc71b6","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"7009cce913","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"文化部办公厅提供"}],"contents":[{"id":"7d2ada26e6","type":"title","text":"江青张春桥姚文元在批判《园丁之歌》稿件上的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba4504fc81","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb921525fc","type":"paragraph","text":"《园丁之歌，剧名就不合适，园丁应是共产党，怎么是教师、知识分子呢？","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a3c1f68aee","type":"paragraph","text":"教育路线也有问题。学生受教师摆布。（剧中的）女教师热爱工农，最后又给小孩子出了难题。还是让孩子成为火车司机好。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"02bea183a4","type":"paragraph","text":"（剧中的）教室看不出典型环境来。女教师还给男教师说好话。男教师转变也不合理。“没有文化怎能担起革命重担”，这句话问题大了。什么没文化就不能干革命。简直是反攻倒算。应是有文化更好革命。女的表演简直是青衣花旦，化妆象少奶奶。矛盾也没有很好解决。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"613c3090bf","type":"paragraph","text":"附件：","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fc337c37cb","type":"paragraph","text":"江青、张春桥、姚文元在批判《园丁之歌》稿件上的批示","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f91d2c4f7","type":"paragraph","text":"请春桥、文元同志先阅，并请提出意见。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"55c4abc184","type":"paragraph","text":"江青     七月二十八日","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c51d17b85","type":"paragraph","text":"看了一遍，觉得有两个问题需要研究：","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67089bb298","type":"paragraph","text":"一、是否要肯定教师的大多数是好的，文化大革命中也有进步，坏人是很少数。教育战线上两条路线斗争是长期的，此剧的路线，及其歌颂的人物，都是错误的。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b4390208ca","type":"paragraph","text":"二、关于学文化的问题，在批判这个电影的修正主义观点同时，是否要肯定学生学社会主义文化及学马列、毛主席著作也是必要的。以全面说明毛主席的教育方针是培养有社会主义觉悟的，有文化的劳动者。妥否，请斟酌批示。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3666f97db3","type":"paragraph","text":"（建议改后我们不再看了）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c406cd604","type":"paragraph","text":"文元    七月二十八日","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40e4a61ec8","type":"paragraph","text":"同意文元同志意见，可以考虑先发两篇，看看反映再发别的文章。文章不多，在质量。批周赤萍小册子，一篇文章就收效。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ea1ce06bd","type":"paragraph","text":"春桥    七月二十八日","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3cd6bc0ce1","type":"paragraph","text":"同意春桥、文元同志意见，请照办。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40b1883b65","type":"paragraph","text":"江青    七月二十八日","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4f949ca092","type":"paragraph","text":"（文化部办公厅提供）","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"deeacc71b6","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}